57
00:03:59,670 --> 00:04:00,160
Ayah.

58
00:04:00,550 --> 00:04:02,260
Anda paham sekali
tentang Master Roh.

59
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,300
Saat melatih Roh Pelindung,…

60
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:08,700
…jangan lupakan Serangan Xuan Tian
dalam waktu bersamaan.

61
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:10,750
Aku tahu.

62
00:04:11,670 --> 00:04:12,490
Pergilah.

63
