91
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,720
Tenanglah, saudara.

92
00:06:53,110 --> 00:06:55,720
Ada yang merekomendasikan,
jadi kami datang untuk mendaftar.

93
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,320
