103
00:07:10,950 --> 00:07:11,830
-Kau…
-Jangan!

104
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:15,230
Namun, Tang San ada rekomendasi
dari Balai Roh Pelindung.

105
00:07:15,230 --> 00:07:15,880
