106
00:07:18,620 --> 00:07:20,400
Ini pelat rekomendasi
Balai Roh Pelindung.

107
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,370
Simpanlah.

108
00:07:22,270 --> 00:07:22,670
Cepat.

109
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:23,790
