125
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:53,200
Aku Kepala Desa dari Desa Roh Mulia.

126
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,720
Aku mengantar Tang San.

127
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,540
