128
00:07:57,270 --> 00:07:58,550
Aku tidak punya.

129
00:07:58,830 --> 00:07:59,440
Tidak punya?

130
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:00,640
Pergi!

131
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:02,440
Jangan!

132
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:04,830
Jangan, Tang San.

133
00:08:05,510 --> 00:08:07,300
