139
00:08:17,550 --> 00:08:18,270
Kau tidak senang?

140
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:19,940
Jangan membuat onar,
mendaftarlah dulu.

141
00:08:19,940 --> 00:08:20,700
Sudah kuduga.

142
00:08:20,780 --> 00:08:22,950
Mana mungkin ada burung phoenix
di kandang rumput?

143
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:24,000
Kau hanya pecundang!

144
00:08:24,110 --> 00:08:24,720
Apa?

145
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,350
Cukup, Liu Long!

146
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,250
Tuan Muda Xiao.

147
00:08:28,340 --> 00:08:29,860
-Dia…
-Aku sudah mendengar semuanya.

148
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:31,480
Apa murid Akademi Nuoding…

149
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:34,040
…boleh menindas yang lebih lemah
dan orang tua?

150
00:08:34,040 --> 00:08:34,600
Aku…

151
00:08:36,270 --> 00:08:37,200
Jangan marah, Pak.

152
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:38,900
Aku mewakilinya meminta maaf.

153
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,670
Tidak apa.

154
00:08:42,110 --> 00:08:43,030
Kau anak baru, bukan?

155
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:44,320
Margaku Xiao.

156
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:48,350
Namaku Tang San.

157
00:08:48,350 --> 00:08:49,580
Tarik kembali tanganmu!

158
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,520
Kau tahu siapa itu Tuan Muda Xiao?

159
00:08:52,710 --> 00:08:55,550
Dia putra Wali Kota Nuoding.

160
00:08:55,570 --> 00:08:57,640
Pecundang sepertimu
ingin bersalaman dengannya?

161
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:58,150
Liu Long!

162
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:01,960
Selamat datang.

163
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:04,080
Liu Long agak kasar,
kau jangan marah.

164
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:06,670
Kita belajar di tempat yang sama,
mari berteman.

165
00:09:08,710 --> 00:09:09,230
Baik.

166
00:09:10,790 --> 00:09:11,230
Oh, ya.

167
00:09:11,470 --> 00:09:13,090
Aku membentuk sebuah
Organisasi Murid…

168
00:09:13,090 --> 00:09:15,100
…dengan harapan dapat membantu
semua murid baru.

169
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,780
Letaknya di lapangan sebelah sana.

170
00:09:16,790 --> 00:09:19,550
Jika berminat, kau boleh
mengisi formulir pendaftarannya.

171
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:21,200
Kelak kita semua
akan belajar bersama.

172
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,400
Kita harus saling membantu.

173
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:23,960
Pergilah.

174
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,500
Aku akan berkunjung saat luang.

175
00:09:26,710 --> 00:09:27,200
Baik.

176
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,640
Selamat datang ke akademi.

177
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:29,600
Cepatlah masuk.

178
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:31,350
Kau masuklah sendiri,
aku akan pulang.

179
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,500
Baik. Hati-hati, Kepala Desa.

180
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:35,230
Saat libur, aku akan
pulang mengunjungimu.

181
00:09:35,230 --> 00:09:37,110
Baiklah, kau juga hati-hati.

182
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,000
Aku pulang.

183
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:39,790
Hati-hati!

184
00:09:39,790 --> 00:09:40,880
Baiklah!

185
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:47,410
Tadi aku lupa bertanya.

186
00:09:47,590 --> 00:09:49,960
Jika kau direkomendasikan
Balai Roh Pelindung,…

187
00:09:50,030 --> 00:09:52,960
…maka Roh Pelindung milikmu
pasti spesial.

188
00:09:53,880 --> 00:09:54,640
Roh pelindungku…

189
00:09:55,230 --> 00:09:57,260
…sudah diperiksa
oleh guru di depan pintu ini.

190
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:00,820
Dia hanya seorang pekerja
di akademi ini.

191
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:04,760
Tuan Muda menanyaimu.

192
00:10:04,790 --> 00:10:05,710
Apa roh pelindungmu?

193
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,240
Rumput Biru Perak.

194
00:10:10,520 --> 00:10:12,330
Bukankah itu
Roh Pelindung Tak Berguna?

195
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:15,460
Mengapa Balai merekomendasikan
orang rendahan sepertimu?

196
00:10:15,550 --> 00:10:16,350
Liu Long.

197
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:20,360
Sekuat apa roh pelindungmu?

198
00:10:22,710 --> 00:10:23,990
Berkekuatan penuh.

199
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,440
Terlahir dengan kekuatan roh penuh?

200
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,500
Itu memang jarang ada.

201
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:35,650
Hanya saja, Roh Pelindung ini…

202
00:10:36,390 --> 00:10:37,920
Biar bagaimanapun,
aku tetap tulus…

203
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:39,820
…mengundangmu bergabung
dengan organisasiku.

204
00:10:42,590 --> 00:10:43,580
Terima kasih.

205
00:10:50,550 --> 00:10:51,500
Makhluk rendahan.

206
00:10:56,470 --> 00:10:57,760
Siapa yang memukulku?

207
00:10:58,520 --> 00:10:59,670
Aneh sekali.

208
00:11:17,230 --> 00:11:18,960
Ada apa Anda menemuiku?

209
00:11:19,110 --> 00:11:20,580
Perlihatkan lagi roh pelindungmu.

210
00:11:21,230 --> 00:11:22,910
Bukankah Anda sudah melihatnya tadi?

211
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,240
Aku tak melihat dengan jelas.

212
00:11:29,150 --> 00:11:31,230
Aku hanya tak jelas melihatnya,
bukan tak terlihat.

213
00:11:31,230 --> 00:11:32,150
Aku tidak buta.

214
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:33,960
Maaf, aku salah paham.

215
00:11:37,710 --> 00:11:39,690
Kau sungguh terlahir
dengan kekuatan roh penuh?

216
00:11:40,230 --> 00:11:41,470
Petugas Balai Roh Pelindung,…

217
00:11:41,550 --> 00:11:43,110
…Tuan Su Yuntao
telah memastikannya.

218
00:11:46,030 --> 00:11:47,210
Kalau begitu benar.

219
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,980
Perlihatkan Roh Pelindung
di tangan kirimu.

220
00:11:51,880 --> 00:11:53,320
Aku tak mengerti maksud Anda.

221
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:58,990
Dari penelitianku terhadap
647 pemilik Rumput Biru Perak,…

222
00:11:59,030 --> 00:12:01,150
…orang yang punya kekuatan roh
berjumlah 16.

223
00:12:01,670 --> 00:12:03,330
Lalu kau memiliki
kekuatan penuh.

224
00:12:03,710 --> 00:12:06,880
Besarnya kekuatan Roh Pelindung,
jika dilihat dari kualitas roh,…

225
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:08,480
…dengan sebuah
Rumput Biru Perak saja…

226
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:10,700
…tak dapat membuatmu
memiliki kekuatan penuh.

227
00:12:10,710 --> 00:12:13,960
Jadi aku yakin
kau punya Roh Pelindung lain.

228
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,620
Bahkan Roh Pelindung ini
sangat kuat.

229
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:19,510
Segala sesuatu
memiliki pengecualian.

230
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:20,880
Mungkin aku termasuk yang khusus.

231
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:22,310
Segala sesuatu ada pengecualian,…

232
00:12:22,310 --> 00:12:24,220
…namun Rumput Biru Perak
tak ada pengecualian.

233
